SIMPLE: conjectural
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Conjectural
<hw>Con*jec"tur*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>conjecturalis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>conjectural</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Dependent on conjecture; fancied; imagined; guessed at;
undetermined; doubtful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And mak'st <qex>conjectural</qex> fears to come into me.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A slight expense of <qex>conjectural</qex> analogy.</q>
<rj><qau>Hugh Miller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Who or what such editor may be, must remain
<qex>conjectural</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Carlyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conjecturalist</ent>⟦br⟧
